{"tid":277326,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"（經濟）關於貨幣系統同埋假鈔既問題","createTime":"2017-06-09T13:25:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-14T20:23:18.000Z","uid":76951,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7c870a4db79763e522473787ca9301f0133fc6c1","tid":277326,"uid":76951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T13:25:23.000Z","msg":"諗到個問題，如果係某城有個勁有錢既人，有一日，佢宣佈派錢，去指定地方排隊就可以拎錢。最後佢總共派左100億。<br />\n<br />\n以下係一d假設。<br />\n1. 大概有100萬人去咗拎錢<br />\n2. 差唔多所有人都用果筆錢消費<br />\n3. 果100億入面有一半係假鈔，而且係超高仿製，銀行、政府、化驗所都唔會測到係假鈔<br />\n<br />\n咁會造成咩影響？憑空多咗100億流動<br />\n如果加大去到1000億，又會點？"},{"pid":"7c2ff90b05b9e0cc727515d38c606d85afa21541","tid":277326,"uid":76951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T13:25:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a48e690842a1054629c397caddd819523c1c277a","tid":277326,"uid":64449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T13:29:35.000Z","msg":"之後你會醒咗"},{"pid":"c007fca8eab435d05a730f9d57b79f7d58f565a9","tid":277326,"uid":81340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T13:33:50.000Z","msg":"依家整偽鈔難度大唔大??<br />\n唔係整香港鈔票<br />\n整蝗國難唔難?"},{"pid":"d14b9fb2e8e1122cc0b483123905db2706aeb1a3","tid":277326,"uid":76951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T13:35:26.000Z","msg":"假設，唔考慮難度、可行性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e04f448c794a0420b9a722db7df08953295d734c","tid":277326,"uid":1095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T13:41:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家整偽鈔難度大唔大??<br />\n唔係整香港鈔票<br />\n整蝗國難唔難?</blockquote><br />\n北韓都印人仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eda2e0e9b11347522a10b8ed5a930e5118df5ea","tid":277326,"uid":46151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T13:53:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.censtatd.gov.hk/hkstat/sub/sp110_tc.jsp?tabl